{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_28c591578ffeuqNw4fcu8ApEhz","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d73a9e9430015WAIhIdKoIJbTg","parts":[{"id":"prt_d73a9f031001VmmOG7LIpZdk52","messageID":"msg_d73a9e9430015WAIhIdKoIJbTg","sessionID":"ses_28c591578ffeuqNw4fcu8ApEhz","type":"text","text":"## 任务完成总结\n\n### 环境配置\n- **Python 版本**: 3.11.2\n- **虚拟环境**: `/workspace/.venv`\n- **安装依赖**:\n  - autograd 1.8.0 (editable)\n  - numpy 2.4.4\n  - scipy 1.17.1\n  - pytest 9.0.3, pytest-cov 7.1.0, pytest-xdist 3.8.0\n  - ruff 0.15.10, pre-commit 4.5.1\n  - build 1.4.2, twine 6.2.0\n\n### 验证结果\n\n| 检查项目 | 状态 |\n|---------|------|\n| 单元测试 | ✅ **599 passed, 1 skipped** (17.18s) |\n| 代码覆盖率 | ✅ **91%** |\n| ruff lint | ✅ All checks passed |\n| pre-commit | ✅ All hooks passed |\n| 包构建 | ✅ autograd-1.8.0.tar.gz + .whl |\n| twine check | ✅ PASSED |\n| 基本功能测试 | ✅ grad/hessian/jacobian 均正确 |\n\n### 关键命令\n```bash\n# 安装依赖\npython3 -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate\npip install -e \".[scipy]\"\npip install pytest pytest-cov pytest-xdist\n\n# 运行测试\npytest tests/\n\n# 代码检查\nruff check autograd/\npre-commit run --all-files\n\n# 构建包\npython -m build\ntwine check dist/*\n```\n\n### 失败项\n- 无（1 个测试跳过是因为 NumPy nightlies 兼容性问题，非当前环境故障）\n\n**结论：仓库配置成功，所有验证通过。**","time":{"start":1775762017633,"end":1775762017633}}]}
